name: MEDUSA - Can't Fucking Win CD
description:
Medusa
Can't Fucking Win
2011


1. Venomous
2. She's Venusian
3. Sugarlips
4. Tinkerbell
5. Luck
6. You're So Lucid
7. Donna Marie
8. Overdose
9. Pollen
10. You Can Take Anything (But Don't Take My Rum)
11. Divorcing Thoughts
12. Tragic Streak


12 classic songs addressing the battle of the sexes. Compiled by Romesh Dodangoda at Long Wave Recording Studio, Cardiff. Engineered by Steve Ellis at Orion Studios, Sheffield and Simon Stride at The Grand Studios, Clitheroe. Features mixes by Romesh Dodangoda.

The album comes in mint condition in a clear jewel case with full colour artwork including full lyrics to the album.
